OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FCloudy and breezy for most
OL,6,Ftoday, although some brightness
OL,7,Fpossible in the east at first. Rain
OL,8,Fwill steadily move eastwards through
OL,9,Fthe day, although staying largely dry
OL,10,Fin the far south. Temperatures around
OL,11,Faverage for the time of year.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FRain clears to the east
OL,14,Ftonight, although outbreaks of drizzle
OL,15,Fwill continue over western hills.
OL,16,FStaying cloudy and breezy, with
OL,17,Ftemperatures holding up above freezing.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
