OL,4,
OL,5,CTuesday:FCloudy across the UK at
OL,6,Ffirst, but gradually turning brighter
OL,7,Facross much of England and Wales
OL,8,Fthrough the day. Staying cloudy in the
OL,9,Fnorth with further outbreaks of rain.
